---

## ğŸš« Common Errors & Solutions

| Error            | Cause                 | Solution           |
| ---------------- | --------------------- | ------------------ |
| CIDR overlap     | Subnet already exists | Choose a new CIDR  |
| CIDR outside VPC | Wrong IP range        | Use VPC CIDR       |
| No internet      | Missing IGW route     | Update route table |

---

## ğŸ“š Key Learnings

* Subnets divide a VPC into smaller networks
* Public subnets require Internet Gateway
* Private subnets use NAT Gateway for outbound access
* Proper CIDR planning avoids conflicts

